<header class='hero'><div class='container'><h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1><p>Replies to inquiries about Jack Travels initiatives and services.</p></div></header>
<section class='section container'>

<div class='card'>
<h3>Which adventure levels can join events?</h3>
<p>Jack Travels invites travelers of all kinds! We organize trips for individual explorers, pairs, families, and corporate teams.</p>
</div>

<div class='card'>
<h3>How can I register for events?</h3>
<p>Event registration is available through our website or on-site. We offer individual sign-ups and team discounts at affordable prices.</p>
</div>

<div class='card'>
<h3>Do you host team events and corporate competitions?</h3>
<p>Absolutely! We organize special competitions for companies and professional groups. Contact us to book your gathering and customize the event format.</p>
</div>

<div class='card'>
<h3>Is the venue accessible for participants of all skill levels?</h3>
<p>Our facilities are completely welcoming and our experts are prepared to help all entrants. Please indicate any accessibility needs when booking.</p>
</div>

<div class='card'>
<h3>What rules and guidelines govern the competitions?</h3>
<p>We follow established snooker rules and maintain high tournament standards. Qualified referees and regulation adherence ensure equitable and spirited play.</p>
</div>

</section>
